{"tid":1421114,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"用高達卡嚟解釋而家嘅事","createTime":"2019-08-06T07:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T14:38:47.000Z","uid":174197,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f4137d1e3917e49e56f64109c4ea2e514998d2c1","tid":1421114,"uid":174197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wm6SFyx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwm6SFyx.png&h=4407bfee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高官明顯無能 無意解決問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LKvHikq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLKvHikq.png&h=2de98961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以為好似斯洛哥咁有料 文武雙全<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wYe5f7q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwYe5f7q.png&h=36012cbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n實際連佐米托夫都不如<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hHxuHNE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhHxuHNE.png&h=275a35ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察上到場上哂頭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jNpMK1f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjNpMK1f.png&h=41a02089&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一味識靠嚇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6VRy9tf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6VRy9tf.png&h=a85a619a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用暴力管治 製造恐怖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SGaHimT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSGaHimT.png&h=3d79a9cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以暴動為理由 追捕示威者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JBhOdVt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJBhOdVt.png&h=fccc410f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n媒體不斷報導警察濫權行為<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vGtBnPb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https:/